Package: UMI4Cats
Title: R package for the processing, analysis and visualization of UMI-4C data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Mireia",
           family = "Ramos-Rodriguez",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mramos@igtp.cat"),
    person(given = "Marc",
           family = "Subirana-Granes",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "msubirana@igtp.cat"))
URL: https://gitlab.com/pasquali-lab/umi4cats
Description: UMI-4C is a technique that allows characterization of 3D chromatin contacts with a bait of interest. This package allows processing of UMI-4C data, starting with FASTQ files and finishing with statistical tests to call differential contacts in two conditions.
License: Artistic-2.0
